show.description: "On the day of her wedding, Ananya arrives at the marriage court in her bridal dress—only to witness her groom, Nishant, marrying another woman... named Shivani. A love story turns into a haunting mystery of betrayal, identity, and twisted fate. To know more watch "You Were Always Mine".
